{"tid":2490605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「國安教育日」港警教育學童持槍體驗8·31","createTime":"2021-04-15T17:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T17:28:25.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a451310e42ce39b09597af8886974626a61d6f6b","tid":2490605,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">榮譽瑪雷人？香港「國安教育日」 學童持玩具槍體驗鎮暴</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/phpzVgJz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2FphpzVgJz5.jpg&h=288a09e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生持玩具衝鋒槍於車廂內嬉戲。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2021/04/15 23:49<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港國安法立法近1年，<span class=\"red\">今天（15日）也是香港國安委首度實施「全民國家安全教育日」，香港警察公開表演中式步操，還開放學生參觀用於鎮壓街頭示威者的水砲車，甚至讓學生持玩具衝鋒槍於車廂內嬉戲。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，《香港國安法》去年7月1日上路，港府今天首次舉辦為期5天的國家安全教育日，港府教育局更是「強烈建議」學校舉行升國旗、唱國歌等活動，同時舉辦國家安全校園壁報設計比賽與線上問答比賽。<br />\n<br />\n香港教育工作者聯會黃楚標中學校長許振隆說，「國安教育不是要學生背熟國安法條文，而是了解法例背後的精神」，他強調，學生應先認識國家，再來談愛不愛國家。學校也提供一面留言板，讓學生寫下「支持國安法」的想法，其中有學生寫道，「暴徒們阻滯和破壞」，應由國安法制裁他們。<br />\n<br />\n港府甚至開放了香港紀律部隊營區，讓學生能參觀「鎮壓示威者」的水砲車，<span class=\"red\">以及讓學生持玩具衝鋒槍於車站、車廂裡嬉戲，諷刺的是，港警曾在2019於車廂內持槍鎮壓示威者。</span>香港警務處長鄧炳強指出，港區國安法自去年7月1日實施至今，國安處拘捕了大約100人，其中超過一半已經被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/phpPTdTZX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2FphpPTdTZX.jpg&h=240a5a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生與鎮壓示威者的水砲車合照。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/phppjBYB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2FphppjBYB2.jpg&h=a78866ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">學生持玩具衝鋒槍於車廂內嬉戲，假裝開槍。（路透）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/php3KB2Ql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2Fphp3KB2Ql.jpg&h=d8bd6cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生穿戴港警的防毒面具。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/php1ysGEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2Fphp1ysGEK.jpg&h=bbe8d338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察公展真正衝鋒槍給學生。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/04/15/phpLTalaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2FphpLTalaU.jpg&h=37a5604f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港警察為學生穿戴鎮壓部隊的服裝。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3501306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3501306&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=03ce9b45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3501306&h=a6403d3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3501306</a>"},{"pid":"012304af48f9ee6fda38c9efc6959df66cebed46","tid":2490605,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WwKcYkrDu3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWwKcYkrDu3k&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=bbb9014f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WwKcYkrDu3k</a><br />\n<br />\n港警還有人性嗎？"},{"pid":"74cd07d8c54b616e81e479c64ee5bb021b777e7b","tid":2490605,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"未來，8&middot;31會成為不可說的秘密"},{"pid":"4e40f33b8c1fa3e598109281325562d806194b1f","tid":2490605,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite